ciscoNATExtMIB.name: ciscoNATExtMIB
ciscoNATExtMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-l4l7security@cisco.com
ciscoNATExtMIB.description: This MIB is an extension to the NAT-MIB. This MIB module includes objects for providing the NAT related statistics. Acronyms: NAT Network Address Translation.

cneAddrTranslationStatsTable.name: cneAddrTranslationStatsTable
cneAddrTranslationStatsTable.description: A table of NAT statistics in a managed system.

cneAddrTranslationStatsEntry.name: cneAddrTranslationStatsEntry
cneAddrTranslationStatsEntry.description: An entry in the cneAddrTranslationStatsTable. This contains information about the NAT related statistics pertaining to a module. The entPhysicalIndex specifies the entry in entPhysicalTable with entPhysicalClass='module'.

cneAddrTranslationNumActive.name: cneAddrTranslationNumActive
cneAddrTranslationNumActive.reference: This object is an aggregate of the objects natAddrBindNumberOfEntries and natAddrPortBindNumberOfEntries defined in the RFC 4008, NAT-MIB [RFC4008].
cneAddrTranslationNumActive.description: The total number of address translation entries that are currently available in the NAT device. This indicates the aggregate of the translation entries created from both the static and dynamic address translation mechanisms.

cneAddrTranslationNumPeak.name: cneAddrTranslationNumPeak
cneAddrTranslationNumPeak.description: The maximum number of address translation entries that are active at any one time since the system startup. This indicates the high watermark of address translation entries that are active at any one time since the system startup. This object includes the translation entries created from both the static and dynamic address translation mechanisms.

cneAddrTranslation1min.name: cneAddrTranslation1min
cneAddrTranslation1min.description: The averaged number of address translation entries which the NAT device establishing per second, averaged over the last 1 minute. This object includes the translation entries created from both the static and dynamic address translation mechanisms.

cneAddrTranslation5min.name: cneAddrTranslation5min
cneAddrTranslation5min.description: The averaged number of address translation entries which the NAT device establishing per second, averaged over the last 5 minutes. This object includes the translation entries created from both the static and dynamic address translation mechanisms.

ciscoNatExtMIBCompliance.name: ciscoNatExtMIBCompliance
ciscoNatExtMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the CISCO-NAT-EXT-MIB.

ciscoNatExtAddrTransStatsGroup.name: ciscoNatExtAddrTransStatsGroup
ciscoNatExtAddrTransStatsGroup.description: This group contains the objects for NAT address translation related statistics.
